  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>コハク、何食べてるの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kohaku, what are you eating?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>26</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>さくらんぼミソ焼きおにぎりだよ。
表面に塗ったミソと
具のさくらんぼの相性が抜群なんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A cherry and miso-grilled rice ball. The miso
spread on the surface and the cherry filling
together are wonderful.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>27</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>よかったらシングもどう？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Do you want to try some?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>27</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>え、遠慮しておくよ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I-I'll refrain...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>26</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>それにしても
コハクのミソ好きは相変わらずだなぁ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But still, I see you love miso as much as ever.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>26</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>うん、ミソはなんにでも合う
世界一おいしい食材だもん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah. Miso fits with anything.
It's the best ingredient in the entire world.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>27</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ねぇねぇ、知ってる？
ミソを身体に塗ると
お肌がスベスベになるんだって！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, hey, did you know? If you coat your body
in miso, it'll make your skin all smooth!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>本当に？
さっそくやってみなきゃ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Really? I have to hurry and try it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>な、なに言ってるの、あの二人！？
こんなにおいしいミソを身体に塗るなんて
もったいないよ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wh-What the heck are those two saying?!
It would be a total waste of delicious
miso to cover your body with it!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>27</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ちょっと止めてくる！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I have to go stop them!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>27</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あ、え？
ちょっと、コハク！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ah-- what?
Wait, Kohaku?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>26</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
